SMACSS - Scalable and Modular Architecture for CSS
https://smacss.com/

-Visit the site and go to Categorizing CSS Rules for reference and guide for layout.
-syntax in terminal for sass to run (sass --watch app.sass:app.css) type this on terminal.
-use partial to prevent importing files of sass to css(to create partials just add _ on the start of a sass file name).